{"prompt": "Generate a website for a personalized tutoring service. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Personalized Tutoring</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0f2f5;\n            color: #333;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #d32f2f; /* Red brand color */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50px;\n            left: -50px;\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n        }\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 0.8; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            margin: 0 0 20px 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n        }\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-card {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n        .service-card i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n        }\n        .service-card p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .testimonial-section {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .testimonial-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .testimonial-card {\n            background-color: #f0f2f5;\n            border-left: 5px solid #d32f2f;\n            padding: 30px;\n            text-align: left;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            font-style: italic;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .testimonial-card::before {\n            content: '\"';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 10px;\n            left: 10px;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            opacity: 0.3;\n        }\n        .testimonial-card p {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        .testimonial-card .author {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #333;\n            text-align: right;\n            font-style: normal;\n        }\n        .contact-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, #d32f2f, #e57373);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .contact-section h2 {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form input:focus,\n        .contact-form textarea:focus {\n            outline: none;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #e57373;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .navbar {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n        .navbar .logo {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        .navbar .nav-links a {\n            margin-left: 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #333;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .navbar .nav-links a:hover {\n            color: #d32f2f;\n        }\n        #mobile-menu-icon {\n            display: none;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .services-grid, .testimonial-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n            .navbar .nav-links {\n                display: none;\n                flex-direction: column;\n                position: absolute;\n                top: 70px;\n                left: 0;\n                width: 100%;\n                background-color: #fff;\n                padding: 20px 0;\n                box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            }\n            .navbar .nav-links.active {\n                display: flex;\n            }\n            .navbar .nav-links a {\n                margin: 10px 0;\n                padding: 10px 20px;\n            }\n            #mobile-menu-icon {\n                display: block;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"navbar\">\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"logo\">LearnBright Tutoring</a>\n        <div class=\"nav-links\" id=\"navLinks\">\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#testimonials\">Testimonials</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"mobile-menu-icon\" onclick=\"toggleMenu()\">\n            &#9776;\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Unlock Your Potential</h1>\n        <p>Personalized, effective tutoring tailored to your unique learning style.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"services-grid\">\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher\"></i>\n                <h3>One-on-One Tutoring</h3>\n                <p>Focused, individual sessions designed to address specific learning needs and build confidence.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                <h3>Small Group Sessions</h3>\n                <p>Collaborative learning environment for students with similar goals, fostering peer support.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-file-alt\"></i>\n                <h3>Test Preparation</h3>\n                <p>Strategic guidance and practice for standardized tests, maximizing your score potential.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                <h3>Subject Mastery</h3>\n                <p>In-depth tutoring across a wide range of subjects, ensuring a deep understanding of concepts.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"testimonials\" class=\"testimonial-section\">\n        <h2>What Our Students Say</h2>\n        <div class=\"testimonial-grid\">\n            <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n                <p>\"The tutor was incredibly patient and explained complex topics in a way I could finally understand. My grades have improved dramatically!\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- Sarah K.</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n                <p>\"LearnBright made test prep manageable and even enjoyable. I felt so much more prepared on exam day!\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- David L.</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n                <p>\"The personalized approach is what sets them apart. They truly care about each student's success.\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- Emily R.</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\">\n        <h2>Ready to Succeed?</h2>\n        <form class=\"contact-form\">\n            <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <input type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"Your Phone Number\">\n            <textarea placeholder=\"Tell us about your needs\" rows=\"4\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer